                "germanium oxide deposited in plastic paper"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Ratios of reduced capture resonance integral to thermal",
                "cross section determined relative to gold,with a gold-",
                "cadmium ratio of 1.674+-0.003 and a value of the ratio",
                "of resonance integral to thermal cross section of gold",
                "of 15.69"
              ]
            }
          ],
