                "value obtained from the thermal cross-section for the",
                "isomeric state of Ge-77-ms(54sec) recommended by",
                "Goldberg et al. BNL-324 2nd ed. Suppl. 2. 1966 and the",
                "thermal isomeric yield ratio of Mannhart and Vonach,",
                " Z. Phys. 210 13 1968"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Since the metastable isomer Ge-77-ms (54 sec) produced",
                "by neutron capture decays partially (24%) to the",
                "ground state Ge-77 and 76% of it to  As-77,the",
                "cadmium ratio was deduced from the activities of these",
                "two isotopes,by measuring the 210,215,and 263 keV",
                "photopeaks of Ge-77 (11.3 H) and the 239 keV gamma ray",
                "of As-77 (38.7 H)"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Calculated and experimental values disagree seriously."
              ]
